result.execSummary:
The defendant Reginald D Moore was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Reginald D Moore is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Reginald D Moore was found guilty of Possession of Cocaine/Coca(2nd+) [Modifiers: Party to a Crime], a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(c).
